        <briefdescription>
<para>Allocates and returns the next unique <ref refid="structDali_1_1Ui_1_1AttachmentId" kindref="compound">AttachmentId</ref>. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Uses an internal atomic counter. Thread-safe and lock-free. Call once per logical attachment type and store the result statically. If the uint32_t id space is exhausted, an assertion is raised instead of wrapping around to an already allocated id.</para>
